		<Section title='Experience'>
			<Card
				heading='DevOps Engineer'
				subheading='Zand, Dubai, UAE (Launch of the first fully licensed digital bank in the UAE)'
				date='Jul 2022 - Jan 2025'
				altText='DevOps Engineer at Zand'
			>
				<ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
					<li>
						Managed deployments for the corporate banking portal and payment hub, providing
						immediate support for production issues to ensure seamless operations.
					</li>
					<li>
						Enhanced Grafana dashboards to support the troubleshooting and investigation of
						production issues by adding detailed metrics and visualizations, enabling quicker
						diagnosis and improving system reliability.
					</li>
					<li>
						Collaborated with vendors to implement banking and cryptocurrency related applications
						on Azure Kubernetes Services (AKS), using Helm to simplify deployments and manage
						configurations.
					</li>
					<li>
						Developed a load testing suite using k6 for core banking, corporate portal, and payment
						hub APIs. Identified bottlenecks via Kiali and optimized connection pool configurations,
						pod resources, and autoscaling policies, increasing end-to-end throughput by 300%.
					</li>
					<li>
						Enhanced application security by migrating hard-coded secrets to HashiCorp Vault,
						enabling secret rotation and secure injection into Kubernetes pods.
					</li>
					<li>
						Led the migration of existing CI/CD pipelines from Jenkins to GitHub Actions, aligning
						with updated standards and improving team efficiency by consolidating workflows within
						GitHub.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</Card>
			<Card
				heading='QA Automation Engineer'
				subheading='Zand, Dubai, UAE'
				date='Nov 2021 - Jul 2022'
				altText='QA Automation Engineer at Zand'
			>
				<ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
					<li>
						Designed and implemented an automated testing suite for the corporate banking platform
						using Selenium (Java), integrating it into the GitHub Actions CI/CD pipeline to enhance
						deployment reliability.
					</li>
					<li>
						Developed and scheduled a daily automated API testing job using Newman, ensuring
						consistent validation of functionality and system reliability.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</Card>
			<Card
				heading='Full Stack Developer (Intern)'
				subheading='Zand, Dubai, UAE'
				date='Jul 2021 - Nov 2021'
				altText='QA Automation Engineer at Zand'
			>
				<ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
					<li>
						Contributed to the development and maintenance of the corporate banking platform using
						Spring Boot and Vue.js. Enhanced user experience by implementing new features, resolving
						bugs, and refactoring code to improve performance and maintainability.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</Card>
		</Section>

		<Section title='Education'>
			<Card
				heading='Master of Engineering (MEng), Electronic with Computer Science'
				subheading='University College London (UCL), UK'
				date='Sep 2016 - Jun 2020'
				altText='Master of Engineering at UCL'
