					<li>
						<b>Integrated Lane Change Prediction Model:</b> combined state-of-the-art object and lane
						detection models with a custom LSTM to predict future vehicle bounding box locations and
						subsequent lane changes using only dashcam footage (Distinction in Final Year Project –
						Python)
					</li>
					<li>
						<b>Finalist at the Cisco University Challenge 2019:</b> represented UCL as the lead software
						engineer to create an android communication platform using Cisco Webex (24-hour
						hackathon – Java)
					</li>
				</ul>
			</Card>
